Ego Ihenacho Ogbaro bu oye otu ndi ogu egwu akporo Africano music band nke Lagbaja
Ego bu nwa ada Nigerian na agu egwu
Amuru ya name obodo Imo state
Oruro oru na otu egwu Lagbaja
Ohaneze matara ya site n'olu oma ya na egwu ndi nke akporo " Konko Below, Nothing for you ya na Never far away"
Ya na Lagabja garage mba di iche iche kwa mgbe
Ego hapuru otu egwu Lagbaja ichu igu egwu nke ya na afo 2007
